{
  "text": "We have proposed an improved cuboid segmentation algorithm by addressing the limitations of the algorithm in [CITATION_1] . At the same time an innovative evaluation metric for measuring performance of both traditional and cuboid segmentation is presented. Experimental results show our proposed algorithm significantly outperforms the algorithm in [CITATION_2] . ",
